				<wikidot:authorName>Travalgar</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2815899</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I didn't get it. Then I read the author's spoiler note, and I realized that I still had no idea what this was supposed to be. Maybe it's one of those articles that couldn't stand on its own, and needs to be supported by a mythos of interrelated story arcs?</p> <p>-1</p> <p>EDIT: Whoops. Accidentally posted this as a reply to weiserthanyou's post.</p> 
				 	]]>
