ttp://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebillith" >TheBillith</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518567586" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518567586" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518567586" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thegreatsea" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518567586" alt="TheGreatSea" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thegreatsea" >TheGreatSea</a></span> for crit!</p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518567586" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span>, who <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">brainwashed me</span> realized that this theory about Kerr-Newman black holes could fit perfectly into the Orcadia canon and inspired me to write for it, Wikipedia for being a useful but jargon-heavy educational resource (the terminology haunts me to this day), and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7_gcs09iThXybpVgjHZ_7g">PBS Space Time</a> for being a cool channel with some useful videos on black holes (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KePNhUJ2reI">such as this one</a>).</p> <p>Image sources:</p> <ul> <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Kerr-Newman-Orbit-1.gif">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Kerr-Newman-Orbit-1.gif</a></li> <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Kerr-surfaces.png">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Kerr-surfaces.png</a></li> <li><a href="https://images.nasa.gov/details-GSFC_20171208_Archive_e000049.html">https://images.nasa.gov/details-GSFC_20171208_Archive_e000049.html</a></li> <li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Vespula_vulgaris_SEM_Antenna_03.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Vespula_vulgaris_SEM_Antenna_03.jpg</a></li> </ul> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Sorta&nbsp;spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Sorta&nbsp;spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>This is the 13th god in Bleep's Orcadia canon, who has chained up the Mither and is hiding away from the unchained bits of her on Earth.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
